<section class="story-section"><h2>Losing a beloved pet is one of life&#39;s hardest goodbyes.</h2><p>The joy they brought, the unconditional love, the quiet companionship - it leaves a space nothing else can fill. The Lunveo Gemstone Urn Necklace was created to help you carry a piece of that love with you, always.</p><p>Crafted from premium materials and featuring your choice of birthstone, this elegant cylinder pendant holds a small, sacred portion of ashes - a discreet, beautiful way to keep your furry friend close to your heart.</p></section>